	I confess I've never made one, however if I was to take a stab at
it, I'd make the top pieces of two coifs, fasten them together, add a strap 
and build it up from there.  I'd recommend making a padded bikini to wear under
it.  Perhaps you could cover the edges with rabbit fur or something.  Carrie 
Fischer (Princess Leia from "Star Wars") complained that the "brass brassiere" 
she wore as Jabba the Hut's slavegirl roasted her breasts in the hot sun.  
Wendy Pini (the Elfquest artist) has a chainmail bikini that she wears when
