directly affected by this document for years to come.  I feel very strongly
that it t behooves us all to discuss the new _Corpora_ here and, more
importantly, to write the Board.

It was brought to my attention not very long ago that the letters of comment
received by the Board were surprisingly few.  This saddens me, because the
Board specifically requested input from the Populace on a number of important
points.

So many SCA'ers bitch about how the Board often fails to solicit our opinions.
Well, this time the Board has done so.  So, I don't think we should pass up
the opportunity!  They *are* listening.

So, after considerable thought, I have decided that it ain't worth my time to
excerpt my letter of comment, unless sufficient interest in a discussion
exists.

In an attempt to determine whether anyone's interested in discussing the new
_Corpora_, I am listing below those topics which the Board specifically asked
for input on.  If anyone on the Rialto wishes to discuss any or all the topics
listed, please indicate so somehow (including by writing directly to me).

