as important as, nor heeded as well as, writing directly to the Board.  It
seems to me that anyone who takes the time to work up a posting should be able
to print it out.  If one were unable to put the printout in letter form, one
could always write a quick cover note and attach the printout of one's
comments to it.  The important thing is not to pass up this all-too-rare
