Nauseating, founder of the Dark Horde, better known to the world these days as
Robert Lynn Asprin, successful science fiction writer.

Yang the Nauseating founded the Dark Horde as the antithesis of all the
stuffiness that prevailed in the Midrealm in those days, and as he lived in the
Barony of the North Woods, it was the North Woods that often came under attack
by he and his henchmen:  Good people all who felt other people's morals should
not prevent them from having a good time.  In those days North Woods did drink,
smoke dope, smoke tobacco, fool around, or Have Fun, and by God, nobody else
