screw ups of every king.  In case you aren't familiar with it, the refrain
goes," We think, we think, we think, the king is a fink, a fink, a fink, a
figure of respectability.  He rules the kingdom with Imperium Compound, the
results are plain to see."  This piece of satire was deliciously wicked and
proved very popular .  Every place in the English speaking known world has
multiple versions deriding all sorts of people, but the kings are always
included.  

