mundane life.  Julious is Negro-Irish-Japanese doctor of divinity, sensei of
iaijutsu and licensed samurai. This man is the sole heir to an ancient family
that served under Tokugawa Ieyasu- and I've seen the proof.  I have also seen
the papers signed by Emporer Hirohito recognizing and liscensing him as
samurai.  I have seen his family heirloom swords, I have seen his iaijutsu
