two alternates.  Blunt weapons only, polearms considered blunt.  We had a
stuffed 'trollkin', which acted as the ball.  The trollkin was designed to fall
apart easily, with quick repair.  The object of the game was to get the 'live
part' of the trollkin across the goal line.  This meant that the trollkin was
considered 'dead' if you tore off more than one limb, or if the head came
off or the body fell in two.  Once anyone died (abdomen shots were
considered 'hideous wounds') they had to be 'carried' (escorted) to the
