   When the trollkin died, players could refresh the teams by clearing the
dead; this became an important factor.  The person carrying the trollkin
was not allowed to strike it - but it was permissable to parry with him...

   We tried a couple of games here, and one at Pennsic XV(?), but it sadly
didn't catch on.
   We did find that the lighter armored fighters (especially the ones wearing
running shoes) had to be evenly distributed between teams...

